              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character trudges along as if their boots were forged from iron, leaving deep prints in the mud and waking half the village with their stomping. Sneaking past a sleeping dog\u2014or a bandit\u2014is a lost cause. They blame the cobbler, but it\u2019s their own plodding nature at fault. Speed and stealth are not in their repertoire.",
